original: Koch, Enar Michaél, stadsomibuds-man, Kalmar, f. 29/1/04 i Uddevalia av dir. Henning M :son K. o. Méry Alm-berg. G. 30 m. Astrid Engström. Barn: Arne f. 30, Birgit 34, Bengt 37, Bertil 39. — Stud:ex. i Uddevalda 23, jur. kand. i Upp’S. 33. Stadsombudsman i Kalmar sed. 38. Kapt. i Boll u si. reg. res. 42.
translated: Koch, Enar Michaél, city ombudsman, Kalmar, b. 29/1/04 in Uddevalia to director Henning M :son K. and Méry Alm-berg. Married on 30 m. Astrid Engström. Children: Arne b. 30, Birgit b. 34, Bengt b. 37, Bertil b. 39. — Completed high school in Uddevalda in 1923, law degree in Uppsala in 1933. City ombudsman in Kalmar since 1938. Captain in the Boll and Si. reserve regiment in 1942.
